metadata.description:
This is one of 2,012 unique NFTs generatively created for the Genesis Collection: a series of collectible McLaren P1™s & P1™ GTRs, each with its own treatment from McLaren's pioneering metaverse platform, MSO LAB.

Ownership of this NFT also confers membership to MSO LAB, a community platform established to push the boundaries of access and experience.

The Genesis Collection celebrates the 2012 premiere of the world’s first hybrid supercar, now breaking boundaries once more as McLaren Automotive's first manifestation in the metaverse.
metadata.name: MSO LAB GENESIS #1
